name: SuccubusMix
description:
A sister project of WyvernMix, geared more towards NSFW erotic portraits.

Works well with 5-7 CFG, prefers higher native res (768x960)

Version comparison

(first row: V3, second: V2.1)

(first row: V1, second: V2, third: V2.1):

Doesn't do too well with more hardcore stuff, but maybe it just needs better prompting, let me know if you have good results.

Also let me know in the comments what improvements I could make in future versions.
